I've got neither style, nor class. ;-)

My approach was to put the hooks in there for whomever wanted to tinker
with the style and then put just enough style in to demonstrate it worked.
The only guidance I had was something in the bug report that suggested
"smaller" would be good.  So, have at it and enjoy.
