   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>This is pretty simple if you already have some familiarity with Django and 
Javascript.

When you visit <a href="http://openhatch.org/people/">http://openhatch.org/people/</a> , once the page finishes loading, the 
people on the left appear in a pretty unstyled format.

It'd be better to style the people there.</pre>
   </td>
